{"tid":2096892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多次批評時政　清華教授許章潤被指涉嫖娼遭帶走","createTime":"2020-07-06T12:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T01:04:54.000Z","uid":307711,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa97dd85caaef4c1754ec61087aa18ae88f4b5f","tid":2096892,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"近年多次公開批評政府的清華大學法學院教授許章潤，早上被警方從北京寓所帶走，他被指涉嫌在四川嫖娼。<br />\n<br />\n許章潤的朋友向本台表示，他的鄰居透露當時有10多輛警車駛至許章潤居住的別墅外，20多人其後進入寓所帶走他。不過，許章潤的傭工說，當時沒有看到警車，只有兩三人入屋，又表示自己跟事件沒有關係，但感到很害怕。<br />\n<br />\n這名許章潤的朋友表示，許章潤太太收到警方電話，指其丈夫涉嫌在四川嫖娼被帶走。該名朋友批評這是共產黨慣用的誣衊手段，又估計真正原因可能是許章潤十多日前，在美國紐約出版的不同政見書籍。<br />\n<br />\n清華大學社會學系教授郭于華和北京大學法學院教授張千帆，接受本台查詢時亦確認許章潤被警方帶走。北京律師莫少平和尚寶軍對本台表示，會義不容辭協助許章潤的家屬，莫少平估計，刑事傳喚最長時間是24小時，稍後才知道他具體涉嫌的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n今年58歲的許章潤，是國内著名的法理學和憲政理論學者， 他在2018年發表文章，批評國家主席習近平取消國家主席任期制度，其後被清華大學暫停教學和學術工作。他在今年5月發表文章，分析<br />\n中國在新冠疫情下暴露的問題，呼籲改革制度。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536071-20200706.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536071-20200706.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=652fbe52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536071-20200706.htm&h=a1cb6a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536071-20200706.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b2fc29cbe789154aca10896cd2f1f8bb19b2c719","tid":2096892,"uid":7043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"所有反共都係雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5159c11026f2b9c3ddaaf90872545679176c1a","tid":2096892,"uid":25601,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"b2fc29cbe789154aca10896cd2f1f8bb19b2c719","tid":2096892,"uid":7043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"所有反共都係雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"順我者娼 逆我者嫖娼"},{"pid":"8b618cf5c07ba82cad727ae83b7a89684852b37b","tid":2096892,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"該名朋友批評這是共產黨慣用的誣衊手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6694be6a07322fc707db27bbef6b9a25fe5ac37","tid":2096892,"uid":93084,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"四川合法做雞但非法叫雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7350a2b1907fd44dc69776eada8026c9a40ba4d3","tid":2096892,"uid":307711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"邊鳩個5毛負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b204c19822867067eb612c548901b84fbac27f","tid":2096892,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"中国邊有妓女呀⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed2a78a52045c82de011ee5ca97cf1743b8d0aa","tid":2096892,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"乜支那全民皆雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e99dff8db602484c4c46addc19943f25d0f067","tid":2096892,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>順我者昌, 逆我者嫖娼</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3574e14230080cc744e74ab65db7ddc91a05e2d","tid":2096892,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"之前香港鄭文傑又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb04c3f6941fceaeff7373ebc78aaad0a04308cb","tid":2096892,"uid